    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this impeccably preserved specimen, maintained to the most exacting automotive standards. This vehicle exhibits a showroom-grade exterior and a pristine interior, reflecting a history of fastidious care and climate-controlled storage. Mechanically flawless and aesthetically unblemished, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a vehicle in peerless condition. Every component has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our uncompromising criteria for excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
