    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I\u2019ve taken such good care of this car, it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, and that fresh-car feel is definitely still there! It drives like an absolute dream and I'm looking for a new owner who will love it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take a look\u2014I promise you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
