    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a superlative example of the E46 M3, this specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including documented subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. The exterior retains its factory depth with no signs of oxidation, while the cabin's Nappa leather bolsters remain firm and uncreased. Every bushing, damper, and mechanical linkage performs to original tolerances, making this a turn-key acquisition for the discerning enthusiast who demands mechanical purity.",
